<recipe lang="en-uk" xmlns:lxslt="http://xml.apache.org/xslt">
<title><![CDATA[Brussels sprout crumbles]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[Try these in small ramekins or in a large earthenware dish to spoon out. A tasty alternative to cauliflower cheese that makes the most of the sprout season.]]></description>
<source/>
<img></img>
<cuisine>
